Test Case ID: TC-003

Title:
Verify user can remove an item from the cart page.

Priority:
High

Type:
Functional (Positive)

Preconditions:
1. User is successfully signed in.
2. User in on the Cart page with at least one item in the cart.

Test Steps:
1. Choose an item on the Cart page and click Remove

Expected Result:
1. Item is removed from the cart.
2. Removed item is no longer displayed.
3. Cart badge decreases by one.
